ings be upon him, without having brushed their teeth. The Prophet said, \u201cYou enter upon me with unclean teeth? Go use the toothstick. Were it not hardship for my nation, I would have obligated them to use the toothstick\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33104,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/clean-mouth-teeth-pleasing\/","url_meta":{"origin":33114,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Clean mouth and teeth pleasing to the Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must use the toothstick, as it is pleasant for the mouth and pleasing to the Lord.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 5865 Source: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/prophet-siwak-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":33114,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: The Prophet uses the toothstick often","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI was ordered to use the toothstick so often that I thought something of it would be sent down to me in the Quran or revealed to me.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2998 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/siwak-after-qiyam-al-layl\/","url_meta":{"origin":33114,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Miswak: The Prophet brushes his teeth after night prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night in cycles two by two, then he used the toothstick after he finished. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 288 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33098,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/siwak-miswak-with-every-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":33114,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Using the toothstick with every ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWere it not hardship for my nation, I would have commanded them to use the toothstick with every ablution.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 1260 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/prophet-siwak-wake-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":33114,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Miswak: The Prophet cleans his teeth after waking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, arose at night, he would clean his mouth with the toothstick. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 243, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 255 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u064